Entries.default: "I am afraid my husband is out at the moment. You'll find him in the square."
"You! How dare you come here! Guards!"
"It sounds as if you had a narrow escape. The pirates have been bold of late."
"I don't know what to make of these stories. A behemoth, striding across the land?"
"With all that has happened, it is a wonder we do not have a riot on our hands."
"It is good to see you are well."
"Port Maje has recovered nicely, has it not? It was a relief to see the supply ships return."
